
*0.6*

* Made it possible to use Related with another database for storing node data
* Made sure all redis-server processes gets killed when running tests in distributed mode

*0.5*

* Real-time stream processing
* Related::Node::Query#find

*0.4*

* Related.root
* Custom relationship weights
* More compact key format

*0.3*

* ActiveModel support
* Properties
* Dynamic sub-class loading

*0.2*

* Implemented set operations.
* Added Related::Follower module.
* Added pagination support (sorted relationships).

*0.1*

* First public release
